CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 18, 1955, pg. 15 reads: "Annual Banquet - The hangout room at Centre Avenue Branch YWCA was the perfect setting for the Y Bridge Club's annual banquet last Monday evening. Guests represented bridge clubs of the city.  Trophies were awarded to Mrs. Elsie Jennerrette and Elliot Crockett, winners of the spring tournament.  Gifts were presented to Mrs. Harriet Smith, Mrs. Amye Carter, and to the teacher, H. J. Smith II. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group of Y Bridge Club members, including Elsie Jennerrette, Elliot Crockett, Harriet Smith, Amye Carter, and H. J. Smith II, seated at banquet tables, in Centre Avenue YWCA
